<h2 style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#2E2E38; font-size:22px;">Peman Manke</h2>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px; color:#5D6345; font-size:14px;">Ou pa peye kontribisyon ou nan Sol <strong><%= @circle.name %></strong> a tan.</p>

<div style="background:#fef2f2; border:1px solid #fca5a5; border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:14px;">
  <div style="font-size:14px; color:#991b1b; font-weight:700;">Penalite: -25 pwen kredi</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#991b1b; margin-top:6px;">Si ou pa ka peye ditou, w'ap retire nan Sol la ak yon penalite <strong>-50 pwen kredi</strong>.</div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fff; border:1px solid #d9d6c4; border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:14px;">
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;">Kontakte Mèt Sol la oswa peye kontribisyon ou pi vit posib pou evite retire nan Sol la.</div>
</div>

<p style="margin:0;">
  <a href="<%= sol_circle_url(@circle.token) %>" style="color:#fff; background:#991b1b; text-decoration:none; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:10px; font-weight:700; display:inline-block;">Wè Sol La</a>
</p>

<p style="margin:16px 0 0; color:#5D6345; font-size:13px;">Avèk respè,<br><strong>Priotelus</strong></p>
